test.doc:
*Description*
Verifies that the internal colleague user can be added to the User's table via 'Add user' button.
- *Given:* A user with valid permisions who is already logged in (or has a valid prior session, i.e. has logged into the Admin Portal in the current browser before) - *When:* the user navigates to user management and clicks on Add New User Button - *Then:* the user is able to add Full name, User ID, Email address, Department, Collaborator, Select IDP, User groups, User roles and Save the details successfully.
